'''Massachusetts''' is the most populous [[US state|state]] in the [[New England]] region of the northeastern United States. It borders on the [[Atlantic Ocean]] to the east, the states of [[Connecticut]] and [[Rhode Island]] to the south, [[New Hampshire]] and [[Vermont]] to the north, and [[New York]] to the west. The capital of Massachusetts is [[Boston]], which is also the most populous city in New England. 

